## Manual Override Requirements (CRITICAL)
ALL automation MUST be manually adjustable by production crew:

```typescript
interface ManualOverrides {
  customCallTime?: Date;           // Override calculated call time
  customRoute?: RouteOverride;     // Override suggested route
  customBuffers?: TimeBuffers;     // Override default time buffers
  weatherOverride?: WeatherData;   // Override weather data if outdated
  equipmentOverride?: string[];    // Override equipment recommendations
}

// Production crew can always override system suggestions
class CallTimeCalculator {
  calculateCallTime(
    shootTime: Date, 
    location: ShootingLocation,
    overrides?: ManualOverrides
  ): CallTime {
    // System calculates suggestion
    const suggested = this.calculateSuggestedTime(shootTime, location);
    
    // Manual override takes precedence  
    return overrides?.customCallTime || suggested;
  }
}
```

