## Production Workflow Integration
The app must integrate with existing film production workflows:

### Email Processing (Call Sheets)
- Parse PDF call sheets from production companies
- Extract shooting locations, call times, crew assignments  
- Handle multiple formats from different production houses

### Calendar Integration
- Sync with Google Calendar for crew schedules
- Create events with proper film industry metadata
- Handle recurring shooting schedules

### Route Planning  
- Account for equipment loading time at origin
- Consider parking availability at shooting locations
- Factor in equipment unloading time at destination

